title: City Slicker EP
body: I love this ep Loretta especially. Dreamy wobbly synths.

title: Set do shonci
body: I don't speak portuguese. Not the point of this though. CHEGOU 3 carries and is in the daily rotation. That song alone gets 5#

title: Level Select
body: I think I used some of these songs in some blender renders? Good progressions and not too repetitive like other beep boop tunes can get. Neat samples. The ps2 menu had such a mysterious vibe. Now everything's netflix menus... Anyways, chill music with Polygon Dreamscape being my favorite
